OL,3,CTeenage boy dies after being injured
OL,4,Cby a fallen tree in Stafford
OL,6,FA teenage boy has died after being
OL,7,Finjured by a fallen tree in Stafford.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to
OL,10,FHolmcroft Road, in the Holmcroft area,
OL,11,Fat 6:30pm on Saturday, 2nd May.
OL,13,FOfficers went to the scene alongside
OL,14,Fparamedics from West Midlands
OL,15,FAmbulance Service and Midlands Air
OL,16,FAmbulance.
OL,18,FBut the boy was pronounced dead at the
OL,19,Fscene shortly after 7.30pm.
